{"tid":1408942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂屌 成個輕鐵站都係石頭","createTime":"2019-08-04T18:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T23:14:24.000Z","uid":256678,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"013a26e4dc6048826138a4feeb04b55ef95a01b5","tid":1408942,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:47:51.000Z","msg":"🤔"},{"pid":"51ecc69e800c4ab5da15b8f7213c283baa1b9882","tid":1408942,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:48:09.000Z","msg":"其實有咩用"},{"pid":"75fd76f202cc8d149d64842a97d7c5e026ea5a87","tid":1408942,"uid":256678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:48:27.000Z","msg":"有無人答我"},{"pid":"33abbdaaba59cd79dc2979dc760403f316f64a5a","tid":1408942,"uid":157938,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:48:50.000Z","msg":"全民dm Emma Watson. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/emmawatson?igshid=b5y3xa4gke0u\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Femmawatson%3Figshid%3Db5y3xa4gke0u&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHaRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=9662b927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/emmawatson?igshid=b5y3xa4gke0u</a><br />\n<br />\nIG傳送門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHello Emma,<br />\n<br />\nWe're writing to express concern over an incident involving the violation of female rights that has just happened in Hong Kong. As you may have noticed, Hong Kongers are currently experiencing police brutality on a daily basis during the process of fighting aginst the extradition bill imposed by the HK government. Earlier just now a female protestor was arrested near a local police station, during which her pants were violently ripped off against her will. The police officers made no attempt to protect her privacy which was unacceptable on any level. Since the beginning of the protests in June not one of our local feminist organizations have stood out for female rights. <br />\n<br />\nWe are in desperate times and sincerely seek your help in raising international concern over this matter as we can foresee more inicidents like this one are going to happen in the near future if nothing is done to stop police brutality. Thanks a lot for your time!<br />\n<br />\nA group of concerned Hong Kongers"},{"pid":"19056c867dc41dc7405bf35f961e3cf008d01054","tid":1408942,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:48:52.000Z","msg":"我想知"},{"pid":"49e7cd8ce322d04d7f544a402e51ccdd8ea42dfe","tid":1408942,"uid":23037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c317119b1ec47655f98e1f93bbba86c4e28922","tid":1408942,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:50:16.000Z","msg":"有咩用"},{"pid":"def05ea9aad8c38176c204e388b34d4057c2fd75","tid":1408942,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:50:27.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"925cbabe9dd7a41da6a8aba0a3d1f61dee0a0617","tid":1408942,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:50:37.000Z","msg":"咁輕鐵咪冇得開？　好危險wo"},{"pid":"2ea7b5150a854b13b067bd0639fae8ecc82b77eb","tid":1408942,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:51:03.000Z","msg":"係🙁"},{"pid":"de0951355430fd9bfbff55e510b9938b9e8b7135","tid":1408942,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:51:25.000Z","msg":"聽講天水圍天耀站 好近狗屋"},{"pid":"863271af84039b8eebc0d3709cbb0be5281f1a52","tid":1408942,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:51:48.000Z","msg":"無人識答"},{"pid":"1a42461b0c9e68ecf385e836255469de6400e419","tid":1408942,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:53:36.000Z","msg":"好想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.